## Moonshot Bias

This mission should prefer one genuinely high-upside theorem-shaped chain over a
portfolio of only tidy classification work.

Specifically:

- include at least one chain whose success mode is an exact phase-obstruction
  theorem or an explicit phase-locked counterexample, not merely a cleaner
  dictionary of phase language;
- prefer intrinsic dynamical objects over packet-support bookkeeping;
- if forced to choose between a safe "object audit" branch and a credible
  theorem-shaped "phase decoherence tax" branch, keep the moonshot in the top
  portfolio;
- do not optimize only for bounded negative memos.

## What Failure Looks Like

- every proposed phase/coherence object collapses back into packet labels or
