- the exact phase variables can be written but do not support any honest
  obstruction or construction test;
- the mission produces only slogans like "maybe NS decoheres phases" without a
  concrete invariant, lower bound, or counterexample.

These are still valid bounded negative outcomes if written sharply.

## Established Results (Do Not Re-Derive)

- Enstrophy, De Giorgi, epsilon-regularity, `H^1` pressure, harmonic far-field,
  and standard host-space routes are already screened or closed.
- Tao's averaged blowup mechanism is already reconstructed locally.
